					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Bregalad, my <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?p=41846#41846" class="postlink">4-channel wavetable player</a> does that. It breaks operations into short blocks which each last exactly 21 cycles (using a short delay to use up cycles if the useful code is less than 21). Between each block is a call to the routine that updates $4011. If it were just playing a single sample without any rate adjustment, it each block could use a lot more than 21 cycles.</div>

